name: Soraka ꒰ ♡ ꒱ (LoRA)
description:
Henlo !! (˶•༝•˶)づ♡ Since I couldn't find a Soraka Classic skin Lora on here I wanted to make one <3 Am I the only one who loves art of Sorakas classic skin let me know ( ˘͈ ᵕ ˘͈♡) ?

((This Lora does NOT work for photorealistic models))

This Lora works with almost every anime model !! so go wild with it !! ^^

I recommend keeping the weight very high and using the negative prompt (multiple ears), multiple horns, ((more then 2 ears)) !!

The Lora also works really well with NSFW Prompts !! so have fun with that ! I have a few examples of that as well !! This is not a only NSFW Lora though ૮₍ ˃ ⤙ ˂ ₎ა !!

I used quite a few Negative Prompt Embeddings. I have a few examples without the embedding so don't worry if you don't have all of them (´｡• ◡ •｡`).

I had so much fun making the Lora and generating the images I hope you have as much fun as I did ⸜(｡˃ ᵕ ˂ )⸝♡ !!!

Please be kind with this Lora ♡

modelVersions.name: Soraka_V1
modelVersions.description:
I highly recommend using the trigger word Soraka_Classic,yellow_sclera, body_tattoos.

I also highly recommend keeping the weight very high (0.98-1) and using the negative prompts: (multiple ears), multiple horns, ((more then 2 ears)) !!

Optional but if you want large breast i reccomend using Large_breast trigger !!

Here are all the settings used for most the examples:

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras

CFG scale: 5.5

Size: 512x632

Clip skip: 2

Hires upscale: 2

Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+

Discard penultimate sigma: True,

This Lora loves giving multiple ears and horns !! so please prompt as needed i hope this Lora can still fit your needs beyond that though !! <3

If you have any issues please tell me and ill try and help !! ૮₍ ˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶ ₎ა
